title: Midlevel court upholds New York's tougher gun law
text: ALBANY, N.Y. (AP) - A midlevel court has rejected a challenge to New York's new gun law, dismissing arguments it was pushed through the state Legislature improperly and that its restrictions violate the Second Amendment.
